(text "Newer Revisions of the X32 are using two separate ICs for AUX_DA (TI PCM1690) and AUX_AD (Midas M8000)" (rect 1784 -16 2410 -3)(font "Intel Clear" (font_size 8)))
(text "CS2000 = external PLL IC" (rect 128 128 276 141)(font "DejaVu Sans Condensed" (font_size 8)))
